{
  "title": "ReFi Roundup #48: Gitcoin Alpha & ReFi Davos ⭐🏔️⛷️",
  "slug": "refi-roundup-48",
  "html": "<p><em>Happy Friday Regens, </em><a href=\"https://twitter.com/linggih_ngurah?t=tG04Tv0kmB78ym39ANaBpQ&amp;s=09\"><em>Nura</em></a><em> here with the latest ReFi Roundup </em>😊 <em>I'm a sustainability tech professional by day, and ReFi writer @</em><a href=\"https://enjoytheweather.substack.com/\"><em>enjoytheweather</em></a><em> by night. Let's dive in… </em></p><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://go.gitcoin.co/blog/announcing-the-gitcoin-alpha-round\"><img src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/8v315G8ZfHiv2bbS03ECgmdHuIwlk0dw2lfRJfbTw3NnE-ODmFy6kynPoLtAi31ok9BxPFHwe4ef7FVUvDBYp73Aa-FTEhV4_acbU7NZ0QKkGUuBY9alcewHzruweGpfLaQ8McTfADo_SlK8mLlstSHFQ5iza4t6XSTkXJOfunp1eWjTS5HEY745Lue5Xw\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"624\" height=\"345\"></a></figure><h1 id=\"gitcoin-alpha-round-%E2%AD%90\">Gitcoin Alpha Round  ⭐</h1><p>This year started with a surge of excitement around the new <a href=\"https://go.gitcoin.co/blog/announcing-the-gitcoin-alpha-round\">Gitcoin Alpha Round</a> that launched this week. Supporting grantees in Open Source, Ethereum Infrastructure, and Climate Solutions, with a total matching pool of $1M! </p><p>Within <a href=\"https://grant-explorer.gitcoin.co/#/round/1/0x1b165fe4da6bc58ab8370ddc763d367d29f50ef0\">Climate Solutions</a>, there are 50 awesome projects, including our friends at <a href=\"https://www.refispring.com/\">ReFi Spring</a> and our newly launched <a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/introducing-the-refi-commons/?ref=refi-roundup-newsletter\">ReFi Commons</a> project with <a href=\"https://commonsstack.org/\">Commons Stack</a>, plus many other exciting projects in regenerative agriculture, renewable energy, Web3 education, and many more. Make sure to support as many of them as you can! 👇</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://grant-explorer.gitcoin.co/#/round/1/0x1b165fe4da6bc58ab8370ddc763d367d29f50ef0\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Support Climate Solutions</a></div><h3 id=\"whats-so-special-about-this-round\">What's so special about this round?</h3><p><a href=\"https://go.gitcoin.co/blog/introduction-to-grants-protocol\"><strong>A New Decentralized Protocol</strong></a>: the Gitcoin DAO has been building and testing a permission-less and open source grants protocol. After successful test rounds with UNICEF and Fantom last December (<a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/refi-roundup-44/\">Covered in ReFi roundup #44</a>), the new protocol is up and running with the <a href=\"https://go.gitcoin.co/blog/announcing-the-gitcoin-alpha-round\">Alpha Round</a> this week. The idea is for for any project or community to be able to openly use it's <a href=\"https://wtfisqf.com/\">quadratic funding</a> mechanism in their own ways, and build on top of the protocol. If Gitcoin were a garden, it’s now open for anyone to cultivate and blossom 🌼.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://go.gitcoin.co/blog/introduction-to-grants-protocol\"><img src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/p4dDXi5y1XqaRDbMDlGnuparXOkQWSTcYLBrvGAn2hmHIfWLjTdILpfg9JZqcONHHAmI4JOJsf6PKs5fRLEzP8x6g5lDRnlfQwcgev59RtVq3LvqwTFIp48PqZxq01MNHK5XpKeNjdGL-Z3xYFJA2BKMtgPpKUvp1eQBin4a5NnZSbxlcOvoVuugtFYRlA\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"624\" height=\"312\"></a></figure><p><a href=\"https://passport.gitcoin.co/\"><strong>Updated Gitcoin Passport</strong>:</a> The gitcoin passport is a <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sybil_attack\">sybil resistance</a> tool for controlling access to a project or community and rewarding contributors with recognition \"stamps\", while still protecting privacy. If you haven’t gotten your Gitcoin passport yet, check out the thread below and claim your passport <a href=\"https://passport.gitcoin.co/\">here</a> 🪪.</p><p>Some users have experienced difficulties ase a result of the high volume of requests for passport stamps, so please remember: This is Gitcoin <em>Alpha!</em></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">gm to everyone who has created a <a href=\"https://twitter.com/gitcoinpassport?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@GitcoinPassport</a> to increase their matching in the Gitcoin Program Alpha Round 🫡<br><br>Here&#39;s a quick thread on why Passport was SO important for us to integrate in the Round 🧵 <a href=\"https://t.co/e9H8SpATDU\">pic.twitter.com/e9H8SpATDU</a></p>&mdash; Gitcoin Passport — Sybil Defense. Made Simple. (@gitcoinpassport) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/gitcoinpassport/status/1615721732912078849?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 18, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p>Gitcoin also has a new slick <a href=\"https://gitcoin.co/grants/\">grants explorers</a> and a <a href=\"https://gitcoin.notion.site/ALPHA-ROUNDS-POAP-QUEST-493d64efd08e4b40b11c39748a8f1278\">POAPs quest</a> to win VIP <a href=\"https://twitter.com/schellingpoint_?ref_src=twsrc%5Egoogle%7Ctwcamp%5Eserp%7Ctwgr%5Eauthor\">Schelling Point</a> packages. We are wishing well for all projects in this round and calling all regens to show love and community 👐</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://grant-explorer.gitcoin.co/#/round/1/0x1b165fe4da6bc58ab8370ddc763d367d29f50ef0\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Support your favorite projects now</a></div><hr><h1 id=\"refi-davos-%E2%9B%B7%EF%B8%8F\">ReFi Davos ⛷️</h1><p>The <a href=\"https://www.weforum.org/events/world-economic-forum-annual-meeting-2023\">World Economic Forum at Davos</a> was also happening this week. Where politicians, business leaders, and civil society from around the world meet at the Swiss ski resort. Some might <a href=\"https://www.greenpeace.org/international/press-release/57867/hundreds-of-ultra-short-private-jet-flights-to-davos-world-economic-forum/\">criticize that it’s only for rich people with private jets</a>, but it could also act as a leverage point for change with the powers that be, and this time we had regens on-site to bring ReFi onto the agenda. Let’s see what's been going down... 👀</p><h3 id=\"refi-panels-%F0%9F%8C%B1%F0%9F%97%A3%EF%B8%8F\">ReFi Panels 🌱🗣️ </h3><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/ImpactScope\">ImpactScope</a> hosted a great event on Web3 for SDG: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/climateXcrypto\">John</a> from ReFi DAO moderated various panels with Anna from <a href=\"https://climatecollective.org/\">Climate Collective</a>, Gregory from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/regen_network\">Regen Network</a>, Steve from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/VerraStandards\">Verra</a>, Amir from <a href=\"https://www.mentholprotocol.com/\">Menthol Protocol</a> and more..</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card kg-card-hascaption\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Stacked panel at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/davos2023?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#davos2023</a> event hosted by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ImpactScope?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ImpactScope</a> <br><br>So grateful to be here 🙏 <a href=\"https://t.co/r0c42toQjO\">pic.twitter.com/r0c42toQjO</a></p>&mdash; jE 🪩 #GitcoinAlpha (@climateXcrypto) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/climateXcrypto/status/1615375868108447744?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 17, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n<figcaption>Esther Val (@carapilla) moderating a panel on impact beyond carbon</figcaption></figure><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hedera\">Hedera</a> organized a packed agenda of several days worth of talks around ESG, carbon, mobility, and much more at the <a href=\"https://hedera.com/davos2023\">Carbon-negative Hedera Haus.</a></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">⛰︎ <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HelloDavos?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#HelloDavos</a>! <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WEF23?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#WEF23</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/wef?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@wef</a><br><br>Join us in the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/CarbonNegative?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#CarbonNegative</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Hedera?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Hedera</a> Haus, Promenade 71, where we’ll be hosting events every day in the heart of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Davos?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@Davos</a> - <a href=\"https://twitter.com/AveryDennison?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@AveryDennison</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/IBM?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@IBM</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SBGroup?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@sbgroup</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/DLA_Piper?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@DLA_Piper</a>, and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ServiceNow?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ServiceNow</a> representing! <br><br>Explore the agenda👉<a href=\"https://t.co/XTe4nWGVRQ\">https://t.co/XTe4nWGVRQ</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/sP5UbrU0Eb\">pic.twitter.com/sP5UbrU0Eb</a></p>&mdash; Hedera (@hedera) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hedera/status/1614846470976589824?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 16, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/GBBCouncil\">Global Blockchain Business Council (GBBC)</a> hosted multi-day events as a schelling point for ReFi and Defi, in the middle of the tradfi world of Davos. THey announced the launch of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BxClimate\">BxClimate</a> with our friends from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BICOWG\">BICOWG</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/loa_labs\">Loa Labs</a> onboard!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Regen nerds are taking over <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Davos?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@Davos</a>! 🤓🌱<br><br>We&#39;re here discussing the technical details of how blockchain can unlock a better climate future with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/gregory_landua?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@gregory_landua</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/danhwang88?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@danhwang88</a>, and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/kenbweber?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@kenbweber</a>.<br><br>Thanks <a href=\"https://twitter.com/GBBCouncil?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@GBBCouncil</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BxClimate?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@BxClimate</a> for hosting! <a href=\"https://t.co/sV0aqfhCBo\">pic.twitter.com/sV0aqfhCBo</a></p>&mdash; Climate Collective (@clim8collective) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/clim8collective/status/1615456663011459072?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 17, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/RegenRene\">Rene</a> from <a href=\"calendar.google.com/calendar/u/0/r/week?hl=en&amp;es=1&amp;sf=true\">Celo</a> green pilling the world in a CNBC event \"Great Crypto Reset\" 👏</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">From Davos, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RegenRene?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@RegenRene</a> discusses the &quot;Great Crypto Reset&quot; &amp; ReFi in 2023 for <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CNBC?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@cnbc</a> with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MParlikar?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@MParlikar</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/gronager?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@gronager</a>, moderated by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ArjunKharpal?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ArjunKharpal</a>.<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WEF23?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#WEF23</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/CNBCxWEF23?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#CNBCxWEF23</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/4O0HuDFr9w\">pic.twitter.com/4O0HuDFr9w</a></p>&mdash; Celo (@CeloOrg) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CeloOrg/status/1615737950884487176?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 18, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/CoinDesk\">CoinDesk</a>'s session on Web3’s approach to climate:</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">COMING UP: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Davos2023?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Davos2023</a> is abuzz about the post-FTX &quot;real-world use case.&quot; Join <a href=\"https://twitter.com/geisenbergerwes?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@geisenbergerwes</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RRansil?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@rransil</a>,  <a href=\"https://twitter.com/W_Alasdair?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@W_Alasdair</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/el33th4xor?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@el33th4xor</a> and moderator <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mikejcasey?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@mikejcasey</a> for the sustainability use case for blockchain, live from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WEF23?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#WEF23</a>.<br><br>Set your reminder: <a href=\"https://t.co/Flf6wx82Nh\">https://t.co/Flf6wx82Nh</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/WSm5xJpsS2\">pic.twitter.com/WSm5xJpsS2</a></p>&mdash; CoinDesk (@CoinDesk) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CoinDesk/status/1616079040703512577?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 19, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h3 id=\"takeaways\">Takeaways</h3><p>Events like these are a great way to share ReFi with the world and a great place for builders to meet IRL and create meaningful connections. For example, we saw the launch of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BxClimate\">Blockchain x Climate Leadership Network (BxClimate)</a>. Connecting organizations in Web2, Web3, and the non-profit sector to collectively work on the most pressing issues around climate and the environment.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Against the backdrop of the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/climatecrisis?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#climatecrisis</a>, the Blockchain x Climate Leadership Network (BxC) announces the launch of its organization at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/GBBCouncil?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@GBBCouncil</a>’s 6th Annual Blockchain Central at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Davos?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Davos</a><br><br>🧵 1/7 <a href=\"https://t.co/UquGEmTauK\">pic.twitter.com/UquGEmTauK</a></p>&mdash; Blockchain x Climate Leadership Network (BxC) (@BxClimate) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BxClimate/status/1615378611959390212?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 17, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p>Here's to ReFi making it further into the mainstream this year 🥂</p><hr><h1 id=\"refidaocom-updates\"><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/\">ReFiDAO.com</a> Updates... </h1><p>ReFi DAO has been maintaining the largest open-source directory for ReFi projects since 2021. Inspired by the <a href=\"https://speedandscale.com/tracker/\">Speed and Scale methodology</a>, it aims to map the work of projects in the ReFi ecosystem according to some key impact areas.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-20-at-2.22.43-pm.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1155\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-20-at-2.22.43-pm.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-20-at-2.22.43-pm.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-20-at-2.22.43-pm.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w2400/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-20-at-2.22.43-pm.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>It also has the potential to help surface new and exciting projects, and with that in mind, we have recently implemented some changes...</p><ul><li><strong>Voting</strong>: In order to create a more dynamic space, we will now be resetting the voting counter each week. The voting system should not be seen as categoric rankings but as a fun and informal way to surface energy around new projects each week and combat the formation of static lists. Resetting will fall in line with the weekly Roundup where we will celebrate  🚀</li><li><strong>Accounts</strong>: A new accounts system will enable submission of projects and upvoting features, and will also form the base of <u>new functionality coming soon</u>... 👀</li></ul><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/account-welcome\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-20-at-2.38.34-pm.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1187\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-20-at-2.38.34-pm.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-20-at-2.38.34-pm.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-20-at-2.38.34-pm.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w2400/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-20-at-2.38.34-pm.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><p>So with the votes now reset, head over to <a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/\">refidao.com</a> to cast yours now! </p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/projects\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Cast Votes!</a></div><p><em>Got any feedback, comments or ideas? We would love to hear from you - reach out to <a href=\"https://linktr.ee/montybryant\">Monty Merlin</a> - <a href=\"mailto:monty@refidao.com\">monty@refidao.com</a> :)</em></p><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-6.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-6.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-podcasts-%F0%9F%8E%99%EF%B8%8F\">ReFi Podcasts 🎙️</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"emtop-audio-and-video-content-from-creators-across-the-web-em%F0%9F%98%8A\"><em>Top audio and video content from creators across the web </em>😊</h3></div><p>The next round of <a href=\"https://podcast.refidao.com/\">ReFi Podcast</a> (season 3) is coming soon, but in the meantime, check out some of these podcasts from regen frens👇🏼</p><ul><li> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j_BoBiBktc4&amp;t=1230s\">The Gitcoin Alpha Round</a> with the Gitcoin team  🏛️ | Greenpill episode #80 by Kevin Owocki</li><li><a href=\"https://www.cryptoaltruism.org/blog/crypto-altruism-podcast-episode86-using-web3-to-enable-regeneration-for-all\">Using Web3 to enable \"regeneration for all\"</a> with John Elisson 🖲️ | Crypto altruism #80 by Drew Simon</li><li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zykurkGssUg&amp;list=PLSBEMu8hDfFQgjffuQXdiowlV1I12CwBn&amp;index=3\">Climate Action At Scale With Web 3.0</a>  with Anna Lerner Nesbitt of the Climate Collective 🌳 | The Encrypted Economy by Eric Hess</li></ul><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-6.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-6.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"strongrefi-news-bites-%F0%9F%97%9E%EF%B8%8Fstrong\"><strong>ReFi News Bites 🗞️</strong></h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"ememthe-latest-updates-across-refi-twitter-and-beyondemem\"><em><em>The latest updates across ReFi Twitter and beyond...</em></em></h3></div><h3 id=\"raising-100k-for-the-refi-commons-prize-%F0%9F%8E%89\">Raising $100k for<a href=\"https://grant-explorer.gitcoin.co/#/round/1/0x1b165fe4da6bc58ab8370ddc763d367d29f50ef0/0x0d85d55a968bc9929c4f7ddfef2e6008b4ad8b77be65f7c08e89eab7cb760cc6-0x1b165fe4da6bc58ab8370ddc763d367d29f50ef0\"> The ReFi Commons Prize</a> 🎉</h3><p>A partnership between <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiDAOist\">ReFi DAO</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/commonsstack\">Commons Stack</a> has been announced to see the launch of a ReFi Commons Incubator. This will kick-off with a prize to catalyze  three local start-up communities with three key objectives:</p><ol><li>Onboard new talent and capital into ReFi</li><li>Create radical startup experiments for exponential impact</li><li>Build public, private and civil society partnerships</li></ol><p>Any support would be much much appreciated! 👇</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://grant-explorer.gitcoin.co/#/round/1/0x1b165fe4da6bc58ab8370ddc763d367d29f50ef0/0x0d85d55a968bc9929c4f7ddfef2e6008b4ad8b77be65f7c08e89eab7cb760cc6-0x1b165fe4da6bc58ab8370ddc763d367d29f50ef0\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Support ReFi Commons</a></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Hey, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> frens! 🍃<br><br>The <a href=\"https://twitter.com/gitcoin?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@gitcoin</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/AlphaRound?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#AlphaRound</a> has officially started, and together with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/commonsstack?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@commonsstack</a> we are raising $100k to accelerate the growth of the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> movement. 🚀<br><br>Support us here: <a href=\"https://t.co/nzYYuDMODw\">https://t.co/nzYYuDMODw</a> 💚<br><br>But first, let us tell you more about it! 🧵👇<br>/1 <a href=\"https://t.co/lHo8Hgbhcj\">pic.twitter.com/lHo8Hgbhcj</a></p>&mdash; ReFiDAO 🪩 #GitcoinAlpha (@ReFiDAOist) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiDAOist/status/1615420108700291072?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 17, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h3 id=\"digging-into-thallos-%E2%82%AC50m-deal-withimptio\">Digging into <a href=\"https://twitter.com/thallo_io\">Thallo</a>'s €50m deal with<a href=\"https://twitter.com/IMPT_token\">IMPT.io</a></h3><p>This week, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/thallo_io\">Thallo</a> announced one of the biggest deals in on-chain carbon with an organisation known as <a href=\"https://twitter.com/IMPT_token\">IMPT</a>. Big deals in ReFi are something to be celebrated, but there have also been some questions raised about the legitimacy of IMPT. 👇</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Detective <a href=\"https://twitter.com/robdogeth?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@robdogeth</a> keeping the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> space honest and transparent!! <br>As we work towards building permission-less,  trust-less carbon markets on chain it’s healthy for the community to dig into and question each others words and actions. <a href=\"https://t.co/RvvdH9KwFC\">https://t.co/RvvdH9KwFC</a></p>&mdash; Phil Fogel (@Philfog) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Philfog/status/1615406773971873794?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 17, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p>Thallo responded to the situation:</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">We have a commercial relationship with IMPT, in which we’ve agreed to supply them with tokenized carbon credits that they will then use in their protocol, which is focused on gamification to attract interest from retail customers. The platform is set to go live within a month<br>2/</p>&mdash; Thallo (@thallo_io) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/thallo_io/status/1615302463447351297?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 17, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p>While we are yet to see the full outcome of this, with ReFi set to attract ever more people, projects, attention and capital this year, we think these sorts of mindful questions and discussions are important to have.</p><h3 id=\"verra-public-consultation-summary\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/VerraStandards\">Verra</a> Public Consultation Summary</h3><p>After a half-year-long process (mentioned in <a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/refi-roundup-28-verra-standards-public-consultation/\">roundup #28)</a>, Verra shared the inputs they received. From KYC requirements, on-chain registry, retirement, to NFT fractionalization. No conclusion yet as to what will happen, so let’s wait and see how it turns out...</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://verra.org/verra-concludes-consultation-on-third-party-crypto-instruments-and-tokens/\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/01/image-18.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"844\" height=\"143\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/01/image-18.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/01/image-18.png 844w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><h3 id=\"bloom-network-announces-call-to-bloom\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/OurBloomNetwork\">Bloom Network</a> Announces 'Call to Bloom'</h3><p>With 24 local chapters in 10 countries and 30,000 people active on the ground, Bloom has been doing some incredible work in mobilising action.  Now they are inviting people everywhere in the world to start <a href=\"https://bloomnetwork.earth/startLocal\">Local Bloom</a> groups with the goal to massively scale climate action and increase wellness in every watershed and life on the planet. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">🌱 Have you been wanting to start a local community project around climate or social repair? Bloom Network helps you get started from A to Z! <br><br>👋🏾  Start your Local Bloom by following the guide here: <a href=\"https://t.co/Cfm2Z74B67\">https://t.co/Cfm2Z74B67</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/calltobloom?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#calltobloom</a></p>&mdash; Bloom Network (@OurBloomNetwork) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/OurBloomNetwork/status/1615362693023633409?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 17, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p>To help with this, Bloom offer a social network focused on regeneration, templates for getting started at every stage of development, and a global community of local organizers who have experience working on food security, indigenous solidarity, and local economies. Have a look at their <a href=\"https://bloomnetwork.earth/startLocal\">Local Bloom Guide</a> below and give their <a href=\"https://grant-explorer.gitcoin.co/#/round/1/0x1b165fe4da6bc58ab8370ddc763d367d29f50ef0/0x29ebfa45b1d708eda13c20e04a999053361a809a89c48041ffe67890329aefd1-0x1b165fe4da6bc58ab8370ddc763d367d29f50ef0\">Gitcoin Grant</a> to support their awesome work 💚</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://bloomnetwork.earth/startLocal\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Local Bloom Guide</a></div><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-1.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-1.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-events-%F0%9F%AA%A9\">ReFi Events 🪩</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"emget-your-refi-on-with-friends-in-person-and-onlineem\"><em>Get your ReFi on with friends in-person and online...</em></h3><a href=\"https://refispring.com/\" class=\"kg-header-card-button\">View more</a></div><h2 id=\"looking-forward-%F0%9F%93%8D\">Looking Forward 📍<br></h2><h3 id=\"solarpunk-austria-%F0%9F%8C%84\"><a href=\"https://gqcca.notion.site/Solarpunk-NOW-59b0645dafb248afbc1c7bd6f89dd2d1\">Solarpunk Austria</a> 🌄</h3><p><strong>(1st-7th April, Austrian alps):</strong> A fun week of ReFi, Permaculture, and IOT.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">April’23 starts the 2nd season of the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/CommonsHub?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#CommonsHub</a>.<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/SolarPunk?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#SolarPunk</a> NOW! combines a co-created Unconference on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> with hands-on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Permaculture?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Permaculture</a> sessions and an exploration of gardening <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/IoT?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#IoT</a>. <br><br>Read more here: <a href=\"https://t.co/ky6rJBbCHJ\">https://t.co/ky6rJBbCHJ</a><br><br>1/n <a href=\"https://t.co/nIL4vdNFk0\">pic.twitter.com/nIL4vdNFk0</a></p>&mdash; Crypto Commons Association (@CCommonsHub) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CCommonsHub/status/1602684178730045441?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">December 13, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://gqcca.notion.site/Solarpunk-NOW-59b0645dafb248afbc1c7bd6f89dd2d1\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Register here</a></div><h3 id=\"blockchain-africa-%F0%9F%8C%8D\"><a href=\"https://t.co/NVZYEiS0JN\">Blockchain Africa</a> 🌍</h3><p><strong>(16th-17th March, Johannesburg, South Africa):</strong> Rene from Celo will talk about \"Why ReFi is the Future of Web3\".</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">📢We are delighted to welcome <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RegenRene?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@RegenRene</a>, Co-Founder of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CeloOrg?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@CeloOrg</a> and President at Celo Foundation, as a Keynote Speaker at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Blockchain?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Blockchain</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Africa?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Africa</a> Conference 2023: Ready for Business <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/BAC2023?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#BAC2023</a>!<br><br>Rene will discuss &#39;Why <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> is the Future of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Web3?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Web3</a>&#39;.<br><br>🎟️<a href=\"https://t.co/NVZYEiS0JN\">https://t.co/NVZYEiS0JN</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/Co5js30QZz\">pic.twitter.com/Co5js30QZz</a></p>&mdash; Bitcoin Events (@BlockchainZA) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BlockchainZA/status/1615652832195010562?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 18, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blockchainafrica.co/register/\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Get tickets</a></div><hr><h2 id=\"event-retrospectives-%F0%9F%91%80\">Event Retrospectives 👀<br></h2><h3 id=\"desci-london-%F0%9F%A7%AC\">DeSci London 🧬</h3><p>Our very own <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MontyMerlin\">Monty Bryant</a> was speaking at <a href=\"https://www.desci.london/\">DeSci London</a> conference last weekend!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Spoke at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/DesciLondon?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@DesciLondon</a> yesterday at their two-day mega-conference in London. <br><br>Super exciting to see an amazing community of Scientists and experts emerging into the world of Web3. <br><br>Big things to come and lots of potential for cross-over and collaboration with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a>!  🧑‍🔬🔬🧪 <a href=\"https://t.co/8lQLy5cnlP\">https://t.co/8lQLy5cnlP</a></p>&mdash; Monty (🧙) Bryant (@MontyMerlin) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MontyMerlin/status/1615298783792824323?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 17, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p>Looks set for much more to come at the intersection of DeSci x ReFi this year..</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Coming back with a notebook full of brilliant ideas and innovations after 2 days at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/DesciLondon?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@DesciLondon</a><br><br>Funding disruptive research in science and the commons is going to get much easy in a foreseeable future. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/DeSci?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#DeSci</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a><br><br>⬇️ A little overview of how <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hypercerts?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@hypercerts</a> works <a href=\"https://t.co/EkF6ejK0Sa\">pic.twitter.com/EkF6ejK0Sa</a></p>&mdash; Martin Demoustier (@Mn_Brault) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Mn_Brault/status/1615387377119133704?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 17, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h3 id=\"celo-turkey-greenpilling-ankara\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/TrCelo\">Celo Turkey</a> Greenpilling Ankara</h3><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Yesterday, we tried to greenpill people in Ankara. We had a nice chat about <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/impact?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#impact</a> while hosting <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TrCelo?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@TrCelo</a>&#39;s block party.<br><br>Praise dear <a href=\"https://twitter.com/0xumitm3?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@0xumitm3</a>  for his great effort while organizing the event together 🍻<br><br>Special thanks <a href=\"https://twitter.com/0xTuzun?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@0xTuzun</a> for joining us 💚 <a href=\"https://t.co/abVqQAhJLP\">pic.twitter.com/abVqQAhJLP</a></p>&mdash; Abdullah Sezer Kayapınar (@0xJulCaesar) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/0xJulCaesar/status/1614563838476656640?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 15, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h3 id=\"future-of-refi-talent-protocol-refi-event-with-celo-and-impact-market\">Future of ReFi:  <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TalentProtocol\">Talent protocol</a>  ReFi event with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CeloOrg\">Celo</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/impactMarket_\">Impact market</a></h3><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">🔙 RECAP TIME:  &quot;The Future Of ReFi&quot; ♻️<br><br>Last Thursday we co-hosted a celebration for Regenerative Finance and the next evolution of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CeloOrg?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@CeloOrg</a>. We have to say that it was a complete success✨<br><br>Special thanks to our friends at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/impactMarket_?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@impactMarket_</a> 🫶🏻 <a href=\"https://t.co/9SBVmSsizy\">pic.twitter.com/9SBVmSsizy</a></p>&mdash; Talent Protocol (@TalentProtocol) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TalentProtocol/status/1615755394223337474?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 18, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h3 id=\"cyberconnect-hosted-a-refi-panel-at-their-new-year-summit-with-toucan-spirals-protocol-and-ethic-hub\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/CyberConnectHQ\">CyberConnect</a> hosted a ReFi panel at their New Year Summit with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ToucanProtocol\">Toucan</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SpiralsProtocol\">Spirals</a> protocol, and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/EthicHub\">Ethic Hub</a>.</h3><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">ON AIR! Our second panel of the day presented by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CeloOrg?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@CeloOrg</a> with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ToucanProtocol?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ToucanProtocol</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SpiralsProtocol?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@SpiralsProtocol</a>, and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/EthicHub?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@EthicHub</a>. <br><br>Join us as we hear from industry leaders on “Regenerative Economy &amp; Web3”. <a href=\"https://t.co/yAZdwGh9EW\">https://t.co/yAZdwGh9EW</a><br><br>Leave questions in the comment below! <a href=\"https://t.co/x2ZYjxrrIs\">https://t.co/x2ZYjxrrIs</a></p>&mdash; CyberConnect (@CyberConnectHQ) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CyberConnectHQ/status/1615453657247498240?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 17, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><hr><h2 id=\"add-your-refi-event-%F0%9F%91%87%F0%9F%8F%BD\">Add your ReFi event! 👇🏽</h2><p><em>Got a ReFi, crypto, or climate event coming up and what to have it featured in the newsletter? Add yours to ReFi Spring! </em></p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://airtable.com/shrKUM3uH0Ph5oEYw\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Add your ReFi event</a></div><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-7.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-7.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"projects-radar-%F0%9F%93%A1\">Projects Radar 📡</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"ema-showcase-of-exciting-projects-on-our-radar-this-weekem\"><em>A showcase of exciting projects on our radar this week</em></h3><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/projects-impact\" class=\"kg-header-card-button\">View More</a></div><p>Fundraising and investing is the hot topic this week, here are some other cool projects in the space:</p><ul><li>​​💸 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/AngelProtocol\"><strong>Angel Protocol</strong></a>: providing tools to fundraise, coordinate, and invest capital. Connecting donors &amp; investors with non-profits, social enterprises, and other changemakers around the world.</li><li><strong>☀️ <a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/solarpunkdao\">$Earth - Solarpunk Dao</a></strong>: currency for the solarpunk paradigm, backed by climate solutions. A borderless, capital efficient funnel to incentivize, mobilize &amp; allocate capital towards climate solutions.</li><li><strong>👐 </strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/Givethio?ref_src=twsrc%5Egoogle%7Ctwcamp%5Eserp%7Ctwgr%5Eauthor\"><strong>Giveth DAO</strong></a>: a community supporting and rewarding the funding of public goods by creating open, transparent, and free access to funding opportunities in the Ethereum ecosystem.</li></ul><p>Check them out on the <a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/\">ReFiDAO.com</a> and vote for your favorite projects!</p><hr><h3 id=\"add-your-refi-project-%F0%9F%91%87%F0%9F%8F%BD\">Add your ReFi Project! 👇🏽</h3><p><em>Have a project you want to add to our database? Click the button below to submit!</em></